Setup syntax for 3D, Order(v/c) (CPU):
./setup StreamingSineWave -auto -3d +cartesian -nxb=16 -nyb=16 -nzb=16 +pm4dev Bittree=True +spark nE=2 nSpecies=1 nNodes=2 nMoments=4 momentClosure=MINERBO thornadoOrder=ORDER_V

Setup syntax for 3D, Order(v/c) (GPU):
./setup StreamingSineWave -auto -3d +cartesian -nxb=16 -nyb=16 -nzb=16 +pm4dev Bittree=True +spark nE=2 nSpecies=1 nNodes=2 nMoments=4 momentClosure=MINERBO +thornadoACC thornadoOrder=ORDER_V

For AMR test (native grid interpolation):
./setup StreamingSineWave -auto -3d +cartesian -nxb=16 -nyb=16 -nzb=16 +pm4dev Bittree=True -gridinterpolation=native +spark nE=2 nSpecies=1 nNodes=2 nMoments=4 momentClosure=MINERBO thornadoOrder=ORDER_V -parfile=test_amr_3d.par

For AMR test (monotonic grid interpolation):
./setup StreamingSineWave -auto -3d +cartesian -nxb=16 -nyb=16 -nzb=16 +pm4dev Bittree=True -gridinterpolation=monotonic +spark nE=2 nSpecies=1 nNodes=2 nMoments=4 momentClosure=MINERBO thornadoOrder=ORDER_V -parfile=test_amr_3d.par

For PsuedoUG test:
./setup StreamingSineWave -auto -3d +cartesian -nxb=16 -nyb=16 -nzb=16 +pm4dev Bittree=True +spark nE=2 nSpecies=1 nNodes=2 nMoments=4 momentClosure=MINERBO thornadoOrder=ORDER_V -parfile=test_pseudoug_3d.par
